        public java.util.ArrayList<Cocktail> getCocktails(java.lang.String filterInput,
                                                  java.lang.Boolean nameSort)
        To get a list of all cocktail which have the filter input in their name. The list gets sorted based on the name or the rating of the cocktails
        Parameters:
        filterInput - Name of the cocktail you want to find
        nameSort - If nameSort is true the list gets sorted on the names of the cocktails and if it is false the list gets sortet on the rating
        Returns:
